com.camerontec.catalys.util.collection

Class SmallIntSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractCollection<E>
      • java.util.AbstractSet<Integer>
        • com.camerontec.catalys.util.collection.SmallIntSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Iterable<Integer>, Collection<Integer>, Set<Integer>

    public class SmallIntSet
extends AbstractSet<Integer>
implements Serializable
    Set optimized for storing small positive integers.

    Note that this is an efficient set for all integers, not just small positive ones, but it works fastest for small positive integers. It can be used for a mixture of integers, small and large.
